Catching you up with my mini luxury digest for the month - a list of my favourite purchases, brands to look out for, hidden gems, books / podcasts, beauty favs & so much more >>>

1. This @ete_india 🧈yellow blazer & the pearl belt are my fav finds of the season
2. Discovered a fab new silver jewellery brand @janvisachdevadesign & these earrings got me so many compliments 
3. Found these gorg polka dot camellia ballet flats at @chanelofficial & how could I not? 
4. Finished reading my second book ( finally ) & @melrobbins I’m a fan!
5. Silk scares for summer are a big yes - this one’s my fav from @hermes

Formed by the Earth over billions of years, it’s not just an accessory—it’s a quiet companion to every mood, every outfit, every version of me.
Because perfection isn’t flawless—it’s real!

What if I told you your hair can be perfect on your vacation too? Found this gem @tashhairclub twirl automatic cordless hair curler & it was truly all I needed to pack with me this time! 

No drama, no extra space, just this compact little curler for that perfect look! 

So if you’re packing for your vacations now trust me this is all you need & hey I don’t gatekeep 😘🙋🏻‍♀️💘

Twirled through the streets of London in the dreamiest desi fit by @rinessa.brand 🩵

Designed in the UK, made with love in India, this look is all about blending bold traditions & modern aesthetics!

Shot this reel in one of my fav cities in the world and I’m lowkey obsessed 😍

I’m wearing - Mayfair Blue De Provence, a couture silhouette with organza over premium lawn, silk threaded embroidery & intricate embellishments! Just apt for the upcoming festive season & all those summer weddings!
